archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.documentation: https://s2graph.apache.org High-performance Distributed Graph Database Apache S2Graph is a graph database designed to handle transactional graph processing at scale. Its REST API allows you to store, manage and query relational information using edge and vertex representations in a fully asynchronous and non-blocking manner.

children.content: The programming interfaces allow providers of graph databases to build systems that are TinkerPop enabled and allow application programmers to write programs that talk to those systems.
